I try with the v1.7.2 toolbox. Using the same environment installed before (sparvio) I can download the data with

conda activate sparvio
./read_log.py --ports
sudo ./read_log.py --retain --port /dev/ttyUSB0:115200bps

Note that the data logger is directly connected with the USB cable to the laptop.